DRA Platform Database Migrations
================================

This directory contains Alembic migrations for the DRA Platform database.

Quick Commands
--------------

# Create a new migration (after modifying models)
alembic revision --autogenerate -m "description"

# Apply all pending migrations
alembic upgrade head

# Downgrade one revision
alembic downgrade -1

# View current revision
alembic current

# View migration history
alembic history

# Create empty migration
alembic revision -m "description"

Initial Setup
-------------
1. Ensure your DATABASE_URL environment variable is set
2. Run: alembic upgrade head

For Development
---------------
When adding new models:
1. Add model to models/
2. Import model in alembic/env.py
3. Run: alembic revision --autogenerate -m "add new_model"
4. Review the generated migration
5. Run: alembic upgrade head
